subtitleNullable: Domino's Pizza, Inc. NYSE - Nasdaq Real Time Price (for 2 Years) in $USD
descriptionNullable:
### Context

Domino's Pizza, Inc. popularly known as "Domino's" is the largest pizza restaurant chain in the world based on global retail sales, with more than 18,000 stores in over 90 markets. The following is the Stock Market Data for the past two years, starting from: 16th October 2019 to 15th October 2021.

### Content

Format is .csv with following features/columns:

Date - In year-month-date (yyyy-mm-dd)
Open - Price of the stock at market open
High - Highest/Max price reached during the day
Low - Lowest/Min price reached during the day
Close - Stock price at the closing of the day
Volume - Number of shares traded during the day

- Price is in $USD.
- I have rounded off the prices to two decimal places.

### Acknowledgements

Data is extracted from [finance.yahoo.com](https://finance.yahoo.com/)

### Inspiration

Tasks like price changes over time, graphing and comparing numerous stocks at once, or generating and visualizing new metrics from the data provided are all possible. Stock statistics such as volatility and moving averages can be determined using this information.
